			</div>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="state-how-it-works--dev">
		<div class="container">
			<h1 class="heading text-center">
				**Warning** Awesome Developer Only Section
			</h1>
			<div class="row">
				<div class="col-md-6 text-center">
